highlights.text: Taylor Swift has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Anti-Hero” is the highest at #2.
“All I Want for Christmas Is You” by Mariah Carey is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 64 spots at #54.
“Evoque Prata” by MC MENOR HR, MC MENOR SG, and DJ ESCOBAR is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #106.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 302 weeks straight.
